data.description: Discover a unique opportunity on this sprawling 2.87-acre property featuring a beautifully updated home, expansive living space, and exceptional amenities. This meticulously maintained residence offers over 4,000sqft of luxurious living space. The basement includes a bedroom, full kitchen, full bathroom, and a second gas fireplace. Step outside to your own oasis—an inviting covered patio that's perfect for outdoor activities. West Pole Barn (100X40): A versatile haven, it features a concrete floor, shed, shop, a man cave with full bath, and a 2 bedroom guest suit with a full bathroom and separate entrance. East Pole Barn (60X30): Offering ample storage space, this barn boasts a concrete floor and a 1/2 loft. Enjoy peace of mind with a whole-home generator that ensures you're never left in the dark during power outages. Experience the full potential of this extraordinary property—schedule a viewing today.
